msgctxt "mn130:5.7"
msgid "So evamāha: "
msgstr "He says, "

msgctxt "mn130:5.8"
msgid "‘addasaṃ, bhante’ti. "
msgstr "‘I saw that, sir.’ "

#. HTML: </p><p>
