msgid "ye kira, bho, pāpakāni kammāni karonti te diṭṭheva dhamme evarūpā vividhā kammakāraṇā karīyanti, kimaṅgaṃ pana parattha. Handāhaṃ kalyāṇaṃ karomi kāyena vācāya manasā’ti? "
